Package org.nlpub.watset.eval

Class NormalizedModifiedPurity<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nlpub.watset.eval.NormalizedModifiedPurity<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - a cluster element type.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CachedNormalizedModifiedPurity
    public class NormalizedModifiedPurity<V>
extends java.lang.Object
    An implementation of the normalized modified purity evaluation measure for overlapping clustering.

    Please be especially careful with the hashCode and equals methods of the cluster elements.

    See Also:
    Evaluation of clustering, Kawahara et al. (ACL 2014), Ustalov et al. (ACL 2018)
